repair.repairedDockerfile:
FROM ubuntu:14.04

RUN DEBIAN_FRONTEND=noninteractive apt-get update && apt-get -y dist-upgrade
RUN DEBIAN_FRONTEND=noninteractive apt-get --no-install-recommends -y install apache2 libapache2-mod-php5 curl

RUN rm /var/www/html/index.html

ENV APACHE_RUN_USER www-data
ENV APACHE_RUN_GROUP www-data
ENV APACHE_LOG_DIR /var/log/apache2
ENV APACHE_LOCK_DIR /var/lock/apache2
ENV APACHE_PID_FILE /var/run/apache2/apache2.pid

CMD ["/usr/sbin/apache2", "-D", "FOREGROUND"]

ADD . /var/www/html/

EXPOSE 80
